Diamond::

she was sitting at a table, sipping on some gold energon.  She was 
staring at the wall, her back to door. She was thinking about why she 
even opened her mouth in the first place. RULE 1, NEVER TELL ANYONE 
ANYTHING, so why did she?  RULE 2, THOSE WHO KNOW ANYTHING, YOU KILL, 
so why hasn't she? She had thse questions running through her mind.  
She also was trying to figure out what programs where her's and which 
ones were those of the council's.  She sipped her drink absent 
mindedly as she pondered her situation.  She wondered that if they 
ever found out that she had the plans to the whole cybertron council 
network.  Including the plans for an energy extractor that could pull 
energy from the planet core and make enough energon cubes to run 
Cybertron for the next 12 eons.  She sighed and told herself over and 
over again, shut up, clam up and don't say another word to anyone or 
your slagged and they will get the info.
